# CLAUDE.local.md

Personal, machine-local notes. Gitignored. Never committed, never shared.
Use this for your own paths, shortcuts, and scratch notes.

- (example) Dev server already runs on port 3000. Don't start a second one.
- (example) My local scratch outputs go to ~/Desktop/scratch/, safe to delete.
- (example) When I say "ship it" I mean: lint, build, then open a PR. Never merge for me.
